Revert Wine 11.11 texelFetchOffset change in glsl_shader.c

Wine 11.11 changed the ld() instruction to add texel offset to coordinates
for non-mipmapped buffer/MSAA textures instead of using texelFetchOffset().
This changes shader output and could cause visual corruption. Reverts to the
Wine 11.0 behavior where the offset is always passed via WINED3D_GLSL_SAMPLE_OFFSET.

